		<title>05SHOPPING</title>
		<content>                                       
    The village of Bomere Heath has a  
 small range of shops e.g. a butchers, 
 a newsagent, a general store/post     
 office. Of the people we surveyed 92% 
 made use of the shops for purchasing  
 small items although 2 did travel to  
 the{hyper-markets}e.g. Tesco's in the 
 Harlescott district of Shrewsbury. For
 larger items e.g. furniture,          
 electrical goods the people we        
 surveyed travelled to Shrewsbury (99%)
 Birmingham or Wem(Shropshire).        
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
